Step 1:
	Collect all the relevent information before the session
  
Step 2:
	Know the business expectation

Step 3:
	Know the gap issue. What is expected and what is shown
	
Step 4:
	Have possible scenarios of what may be the reason

Step 5:
	Invite representation from each team. Business analyst needs to lead the debugging
	
		1) Business Analyst 
				Expected metric
				Anomaly
				Business process supporting the data
		2) BI engineer
				Check the BI Layer
				Identify the entities for the metric/anaomaly
				SQL for the issues
				Example correct records
				Example incorrect records
		3) Data engineer
				data in tables
				Schedule
				Dependencies
				Source application
		4) Source system contact
				UI
				Backend

Not everyone needs to be in the call at the same time.
	multi step process
		1) Analysis of a step should provide charactrizationa and reason with supporting data to next step
